{"tid":147601,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"有無巴打隻狗有行為問題？","createTime":"2017-03-08T03:31:12.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-11T03:45:24.000Z","uid":39210,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"81ca285d5585ccd561228c9da11528ba0575ff57","tid":147601,"uid":39210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T03:31:12.000Z","msg":"我隻柴犬以前都無咁唔聽話，愈大就愈咬野，乜都咬出黎，電線都咬爛幾條<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n打佢又無用 因為好肥，佢完全唔痛， 宜加諗緊上犬訓班，有無巴打上過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c74a40e31827f07445a82846fc38c2208ab5cb5a","tid":147601,"uid":21871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T03:32:35.000Z","msg":"我個隻都係由細到大亂咬野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n鬧同氹都試過,我諗天性黎"},{"pid":"6f6c0a95279620d548c98861cf10fa4ced5c34ea","tid":147601,"uid":39210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T03:38:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我個隻都係由細到大亂咬野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n鬧同氹都試過,我諗天性黎</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  佢曾經有一排乖過架，唔知係味玩具玩厭左 分散唔到佢注意力"},{"pid":"588fcd26e0f4ea47f42593466540be050c13e1f0","tid":147601,"uid":39210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T03:41:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8GYe35P.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8GYe35P.jpg&h=3fda6c2e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/08/114141_69323530da653ba65a7d1457d0829883.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F08%2F114141_69323530da653ba65a7d1457d0829883.jpg&h=9db709c6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/08/114142_480f8fdd30a2af0aba3a8ec1f265d9d9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%