l/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d68e42cb501d0b61f8793d708b2520eb070434c5","tid":147601,"uid":74571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T04:09:03.000Z","msg":"呢個星期日去上訓練班<br />\n<br />\n漁護署搞唔洗錢，不過每次得40人，得閒留意下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d35e9d096e63d0ab8596f9f8bdc23b4608cf48d8","tid":147601,"uid":74571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T04:10:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我隻柴都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲跳埋上餐台搵野咬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n梳發上面既野 洗衣機入面既臭衫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nyes 一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而家屋企d野好多收埋晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce237d17a8f4a7f6bb9b1b1f7b5a2447bef09ae7","tid":147601,"uid":39210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T04:15:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢個星期日去上訓練班<br />\n<br />\n漁護署搞唔洗錢，不過每次得40人，得閒留意下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n正喎 我上網搵下先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n佢已經咬爛抽濕機電線加兩條macbook差電線 唔貴唔咬架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b65824dc60646d3d36a214811abbcadf62ed3843","tid":147601,"uid":74571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T04:18:07.000Z","msg":"條死仔好識揀野咬，一排6-7隻錶，平既唔咬，係揀隻最貴既黎咬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7b686a2b5da1c95785a8251b89ca7edcc43e52a","tid":147601,"uid":88877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T06:09:07.000Z","msg":"我隻衰仔就無亂咬野，但一樣突然變得唔乖。我呢排睇緊Cesar 的報告狗班長，佢主張用pack leaders 的姿態話俾主人聽要stay calm 。<br />\n其實你主人可能覺得咬野好開心好有趣，可能你要俾一些更有趣的玩具佢玩，等佢覺得咬野都不過不外如是。<br />\n如果真係要鬧佢，你要搵啱時間，即係主人個咀一掂到電線，或行緊埋去，已經要NO 佢，要佢行開，直到伏低完全放棄。中途你千萬唔好發老脾，試多幾次佢就會知係唔做得。<br />\n<br />\n我個仔細個時的樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有趣玩具如下圖，中間可以放食物，等佢自己諗方法整出黎<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/08/140834_7b49ad33827c49315b29d866e0feddc2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F08%2F140834_7b49ad33827c49315b29d866e0feddc2.jpg&h=d3660b37&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zSCCU1j.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzSCCU1j.jpg&h=f6adb9b9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/08/140838_e79f875aa5dd2774d4399fee1c9df197.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F08%2F140838_e79f875aa5dd2774d4399fee1c9df197.jpg&h=fcd4b164&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/27ruv6c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F27ruv6c.jpg&h=da10d5b3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"513ccdbf971e192023d5cbf386a651d08d7e889d","tid":147601,"uid":14208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T06:31:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我隻衰仔就無亂咬野，但一樣突然變得唔乖。我呢排睇緊Cesar 的報告狗班長，佢主張用pack leaders 的姿態話俾主人聽要stay calm 。<br />\n其實你主人可能覺得咬野好開心好有趣，可能你要俾一些更有趣的玩具佢玩，等佢覺得咬野都不過不外如是。<br />\n如果真係要鬧佢，你要搵啱時間，即係主人個咀一掂到電線，或行緊埋去，已經要NO 佢，要佢行開，直到伏低完全放棄。中途你千萬唔好發老脾，試多幾次佢就會知係唔做得。<br />\n<br />\n我個仔細個時的樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有趣玩具如下圖，中間可以放食物，等佢自己諗方法整出黎<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/08/140834_7b49ad33827c49315b29d866e0feddc2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnai